import "../styles/pure/main.css"
import "../styles/pure/base/css/base.css"
import "../styles/pure/grids/css/grids-core.css"
import "../styles/pure/menus/css/menus-core.css"
import "../styles/pure/menus/css/menus-dropdown.css"
import "../styles/pure/menus/css/menus-horizontal.css"
import "../styles/globals.css"



import AdminLayout from "../components/layouts/adminLayout";

function MyApp({ Component, pageProps }) {
  const Layout = Component.Layout || AdminLayout;
  return <Layout>
    <Component {...pageProps} />
  </Layout>
}

export default MyApp
